ABOUT THIS GAME:

Power Lotto Wheeler supports all types of Lotto games from Pick
3 to Pick 10 including Powerball and Keno. There are totally 420
wheeling systems built-in to be able to wheel up to 30 lotto
numbers.

Features provided such as wheel table details including % win
guarantee, winners-check details, random numbers generation,
dynamic plug-in wheeling systems capability, print, load, and
save functions for wheel data and winners-check results. Version
7.2 may include unspecified updates, enhancements, or bug fixes.
